########### Copy Command Block ########### echo "Starting copy block" foreach file ( (fromScratch) ) set i=0
if ( -d $file ) then set cpCommand="/bin/cp -r $file (toURL)" else set cpCommand="/bin/cp -fp $file (toURL)" endif
RETRY_CP: echo "Running copy command: " $cpCommand $cpCommand if ( $status && $i < 15 ) then echo "The copy failed, waiting to try again." @ i++ sleep 60 echo "Trying copy again at "`/bin/date` goto RETRY_CP endif
end ##########################################
